    mindsetNote: 'Nonessential software creates unnecessary attack surface. A BitTorrent client is not just a productivity issue — it is a peer-to-peer network that bypasses normal traffic controls and can exfiltrate data or introduce malware. Assessors should check installed software lists during system review, not just rely on policy interviews.',
