    mindsetNote: 'CMMC and NIST 800-171 specify "what" (multi-factor) not "how" (which factors). Know the difference between satisfying a requirement and implementing best practice. For assessors: document the method used. For CPPs: understand that SMS MFA is compliant but higher-risk than alternatives.',
