    mindsetNote: 'Incident reporting in the defense industrial base has two dimensions: CMMC compliance (IR.L2-3.6.2) and contractual obligation (DFARS 252.204-7012). They overlap but are separate. A contractor who handles the incident well internally but fails to report to DoD is non-compliant with both. Know both the CMMC practice and the DFARS clause.',
