    mindsetNote: 'Removable media is one of the highest-risk data exfiltration vectors. No technical control is more commonly bypassed than a USB port. Assessors should ask about removable media policies, encryption requirements for USB drives, and whether USB ports are disabled on workstations. Observe whether employees carry personal USB drives.',
