    mindsetNote: 'The "covered by their own employer" argument is one of the most common misconceptions in personnel security. If a subcontractor employee accesses your CUI systems, you are responsible for ensuring screening occurred. This is a supply chain trust issue that CMMC takes seriously. Assessors should ask for evidence of screening for all individuals with CUI access, not just direct employees.',
