    mindsetNote: 'Collaborative devices are often forgotten in the CUI security perimeter. A conference room camera that is always on or can be remotely activated without indication is a listening device. This is not a theoretical risk — there are documented cases of corporate espionage through conference room AV systems. Assessors should check all conference rooms where CUI discussions occur.',
