    domain: 'SI',
    difficulty: 2,
    stem: 'A critical vulnerability (CVSS 9.1) affecting a contractor\'s CUI-processing web server is published. The contractor\'s patching policy requires all vulnerabilities to be remediated within 90 days regardless of severity. What is the finding?',
