    mindsetNote: 'Detection is not the same as prevention. CM controls prevent unauthorized software from being installed; SI.L2-3.14.7 detects unauthorized use when prevention fails. Assume breach: some attacker will eventually get something past your preventive controls. The question is how quickly you detect it. Three months of undetected RAT activity means three months of potential CUI exfiltration.',
