    stem: 'A contractor grants a new developer CUI system access on their first day and initiates the background check simultaneously. Three weeks later the check completes with no disqualifying findings. The contractor argues PS.L2-3.9.1 is met because screening occurred and no issues were found. What is the correct assessment?',
