    mindsetNote: 'Business constraints like warranties do not create CMMC exceptions. The right time to solve this problem is before it happens — in procurement, by establishing sanitization procedures for devices that cannot have storage removed, and by selecting vendors who support secure disposal options. When the equipment goes out the door without sanitization, the CUI is outside your control. That is the risk MA.L2-3.7.3 prevents.',
