    mindsetNote: 'MSP relationships are a major attack vector in the DIB. Remote access tools used by managed service providers are specifically targeted because they provide administrative access to many organizations through a single compromise point. MA.L2-3.7.5 directly addresses this: MFA plus session termination limits the blast radius when MSP credentials are compromised. "Always-on" is never acceptable for CUI system remote maintenance.',
