    practiceId: 'PE.L2-3.10.5',
    domain: 'PE',
    difficulty: 2,
    stem: 'A contractor issues proximity badges to all employees for server room access. When an employee transfers to a non-CUI role, their badge is not updated — they retain server room access because "they might need it someday." After six months, this employee\'s badge still opens the server room. What does PE.L2-3.10.5 require?',
