    difficulty: 3,
    stem: 'A contractor identifies a critical vulnerability in their internet-facing VPN appliance. They cannot patch immediately due to a production freeze, so they document it in the POA&M and plan to patch in 90 days. Which additional action is required to maintain compliance during the remediation window?',
