    mindsetNote: 'Password history enforcement closes the cycling loophole. Without it, forced rotation creates user frustration with no security benefit. The combination of rotation + history + complexity form the complete password lifecycle control. Assessors will verify technical enforcement of history requirements in Active Directory or IAM settings.',
