    mindsetNote: 'BYOD and CUI are in fundamental tension. If employees store CUI on personal phones, the organization needs MDM on those phones — which employees often resist. The cleaner approach is prohibiting CUI storage on personal devices and enforcing it technically. AC.L2-3.1.19 requires encryption and remote wipe — both require MDM on personal devices.',
