    mindsetNote: 'Event selection is not a one-time exercise — it must be revisited when the system boundary changes. Adding a new system without updating the logged event list is one of the most common audit gaps. Assessors will compare the logged event list in the SSP against the current system inventory to verify they are synchronized.',
