    level: 'L2',
    practiceId: 'AU.L2-3.3.6',
    domain: 'AU',
    difficulty: 2,
    stem: 'A contractor stores six months of raw firewall and endpoint audit logs — approximately 400 GB. The security analyst reports it takes hours to manually search for specific events during incident investigations. Which AU practice directly addresses this operational problem?',
