    tracks: ['CCP', 'CCA'],
    level: 'L2',
    practiceId: 'IR.L2-3.6.2',
    domain: 'IR',
    difficulty: 2,
    stem: 'A contractor with a DoD contract covering CUI discovers a confirmed cyber incident at 9 AM Monday. Under DFARS 252.204-7012, by when must they report to the DoD, and through what mechanism?',
