    stem: 'A contractor\'s employee accidentally emails a CUI spreadsheet to a personal email account. The email is immediately deleted by the employee, who then self-reports to IT. IT confirms no external party forwarded or accessed the data. Under DFARS 252.204-7012, is this a reportable cyber incident?',
