    mindsetNote: 'The DMZ is not a monolith — it should itself be segmented by application trust level. A CUI-handling application in the same zone as a public marketing site creates lateral movement risk. Assessors should trace the data flow: if the marketing site is compromised, what network paths exist to CUI? Any direct path to CUI systems or shared infrastructure (databases, auth servers) is a finding.',
