    difficulty: 3,
    stem: 'A contractor argues that split tunneling is acceptable because they use endpoint DLP to prevent CUI exfiltration from the device. A C3PAO assessor is evaluating whether this satisfies SC.L2-3.13.7. What is the correct assessment?',
