    mindsetNote: 'DLP is a detective and preventive control for data movement — it is not an architectural control. SC.L2-3.13.7 is an architectural requirement. The assessor should test the VPN gateway configuration, not just the endpoint DLP policy. Ask the vendor: what happens to internet traffic when the VPN is connected? If internet traffic routes directly rather than through the VPN gateway, it is a finding regardless of endpoint controls.',
