    difficulty: 3,
    stem: 'A contractor\'s policy prohibits unapproved browser extensions, but no technical controls enforce this — employees can install any extension from the Chrome Web Store. The policy was emailed to staff six months ago. How does an assessor evaluate SC.L2-3.13.13 compliance?',
