    mindsetNote: 'Paper is media. This seems obvious, but organizations frequently invest heavily in digital CUI protection while leaving printed CUI on desks, in open filing cabinets, and in unsecured recycling bins. MP.L2-3.8.1 assessors should conduct physical walkthroughs looking for printed CUI, whiteboards with CUI, and unsecured shredding bins. The CUI label applies regardless of the substrate.',
