    mindsetNote: 'Media accountability means tracking where your CUI is — on which devices, in which locations, under whose custody. If a laptop containing CUI goes missing, the organization must be able to determine: what CUI was on it, when it left, and who had it. That requires a media inventory and removal logging process. Undocumented removals are a finding even if the individual removal was authorized.',
