    mindsetNote: '"It\'s broken" is not a sanitization method. MP.L2-3.8.5 fills the gap between when a drive is taken out of service and when it is finally destroyed. Assessors should look for a secure media disposal process: where do drives go when they fail? Who controls them? When are they destroyed and by whom? A box in the server room marked "for shredding" with no schedule and no access control is a partial finding.',
