    domain: 'CA',
    difficulty: 2,
    stem: 'A DoD contractor is preparing for a CMMC Level 2 certification assessment. They want to hire a Registered Practitioner (RP) to conduct the assessment and produce the final findings report. What must the contractor understand about this arrangement?',
