    mindsetNote: 'Knowing the Cyber AB\'s authority — and its limits — is essential. The Cyber AB does not interpret DoD contract requirements, and it does not review SSPs. Its role is ecosystem governance: who is authorized to assess, who is certified to assess, and what conduct standards apply.',
