    difficulty: 3,
    stem: 'The DCSA Defense Industrial Base Cybersecurity Assessment Center (DIBCAC) has a role beyond conducting Level 3 certification assessments. Which of the following accurately describes an additional DIBCAC function within the CMMC ecosystem?',
