    stem: 'An OSC uses a FedRAMP Moderate authorized cloud storage service to store CUI documents. The cloud service has its own FedRAMP authorization package including System Security Plan, controls assessment, and ATO. The OSC argues all CMMC controls satisfied by the cloud provider\'s FedRAMP authorization should be credited as MET without separate assessment. Is this correct?',
